comments.body:
to avoid grabbing the mutex twice in a row in the request tracker, could call `.CountActiveConnections` only once:
```
        if (auto connections = g_requests.CountActiveConnections(); connections != 0) {
            LogPrint(BCLog::HTTP, "Waiting for %d connections to stop HTTP server\n", connections);
        }
```
